{"tid":1996314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同學告急] 繪畫手足盼製”抗爭主題水杯” 來交學費","createTime":"2020-05-01T01:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T02:06:03.000Z","uid":146717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a43dda677944f4d1a637151cdb53e9606585fb18","tid":1996314,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"原Post：學生設計手足：自力更生，設計咗啲杯希望大家支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996014</a><br />\n<br />\n畫家係我朋友嘅朋友嚟，P牌仔冇得推Post所以沉咗底，咁我就做代言人講解下...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12Ezq2h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12Ezq2h.png&h=d7d0360b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>背景</ins></strong><br />\n佢主要係自從運動開始同屋企人關係「麻麻」，咁大家明啦，一位學生哥同屋企人意見對立係慘過食屎；而Part time錢基本上幫補唔到幾多，加上面臨各項生活費用都幾大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家有唔少熱心人士有無條件嘅資助/助養計劃，但佢唔甘心好似攤大隻問人拎咁，於是佢諗住運用自己嘅設計/繪畫嘅skill去design一啲產品出嚟，至少叫做有付出過。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>理念</ins></strong><br />\n我諗好多人好似我有一刻會諗，條仆街係咪想發國難財，我都好明白大家嘅憂慮。但其實大家諗深一層，假設可以直接搵唔同人士、機構助養，點解仲會有人咁無聊，浪費幾個星期，花時間、花心機去設計去繪畫張圖？<br />\n<br />\n因為個出發點就正正係：如果有得揀嘅話，唔想攤大手板問人拎錢。依個可能係一個好老土而又on9嘅理念，但其實非常真實。一個人有手有腳，花時間、用自己嘅能力去改變現況，係唔應該畀人指責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>產品</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdR6g5O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdR6g5O.jpg&h=274a7ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Kkbtct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Kkbtct.png&h=94c9c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n暫定$99 <br />\n運費$20（優先選用黃色速遞公司）<br />\n<br />\n扣除平台手續費用及成本後，將以設計費形式直接支援設計手足生活費、學費、不同器材等費用，並在許可的情況下支援其他手足。<br />\n<br />\n提示：好多人會諗件貨抵唔抵買，應該諗值唔值得支持，形式類似「你捐錢畀佢，佢送返份禮物畀你」咁當然件禮物都係要自己鍾意啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">預訂網址</span></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/design--51#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiegogo.com%2Fprojects%2Fdesign--51%23%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=ea66f016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/design--51#/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>方式</ins></strong><br />\n網站中間位置選取：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq1qxFA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq1qxFA.png&h=a77c820b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n<br />\n1.明白到網站有純捐款功能，請儘量避免純捐款，支持手足作品<br />\n<br />\n2.實際內容以原創畫家和原設計同學為準"},{"pid":"03cc85225a28b5e3e4615e52fab366649ea50c2d","tid":1996314,"uid":291093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"thx for share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5e83a44ca2b06a341b452b615e97952fac889e","tid":1996314,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2c5492ee9679f4885af6c8b8c8805d91752fb25e","tid":1996314,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"唔係話學生就大曬<br />\n一隻mug賣99蚊加多一蚊有冇刻骨銘心o既骨頭鏈咀賣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a7d9bbc087f6e6dfd2008b5aedd91969e0df6a","tid":1996314,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:29:07.000Z","msg":"推呀！手足想繼續有書讀"},{"pid":"6540bd262af88fb5c95754792cdf1b60d06cecd1","tid":1996314,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"8b766306179ae9118402260c4a0d47df6d667932","tid":1996314,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"入去坐讀書咪唔使錢囉"},{"pid":"793204f2b32d150062aa37fe22b71d12987cac9a","tid":1996314,"uid":302102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"隻杯太小學雞。。。設計過啦。。白底黑線，會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da886d4b613f95cfa516d0366b33bf4101483a55","tid":1996314,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5492ee9679f4885af6c8b8c8805d91752fb25e","tid":1996314,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"唔係話學生就大曬<br />\n一隻mug賣99蚊加多一蚊有冇刻骨銘心o既骨頭鏈咀賣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"你買嘅唔止係一個mug咁簡單，剩低嘅錢係直接支援手足嘅生活費<br />\n<br />\n何況一個design唔可以用成本價去衡量，街邊一個杯$10都有，但Starbucks有啲圖案可以賣成$150<br />\n<br />\n其實出邊買個好睇少少非支那製嘅都成$50+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d292c2707a3a331a3a71edc630fc05dca66acd","tid":1996314,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da886d4b613f95cfa516d0366b33bf4101483a55","tid":1996314,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5492ee9679f4885af6c8b8c8805d91752fb25e","tid":1996314,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"唔係話學生就大曬<br />\n一隻mug賣99蚊加多一蚊有冇刻骨銘心o既骨頭鏈咀賣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"你買嘅唔止係一個mug咁簡單，剩低嘅錢係直接支援手足嘅生活費<br />\n<br />\n何況一個design唔可以用成本價去衡量，街邊一個杯$10都有，但Starbucks有啲圖案可以賣成$150<br />\n<br />\n其實出邊買個好睇少少非支那製嘅都成$50+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我就唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114241c1a6ac7bdb424d28b3b6619eafcece0863","tid":1996314,"uid":201721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"人哋係學生唔想靠人想靠自己係咪都應該鼓勵下，我個人就覺得唔差嘅<br />\n<br />\n上邊班人使唔使一黎就起晒鋼咁<i